subject: World Cup (Skiing)
Skiing
Alpine Skiing
lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn ended a five-week winless streak Sunday with a dominating victory in the super-G in Cortina d’Ampezzo, Italy, for her 47th World Cup title.
